title: Unisex Drawcord Scrub Pants Jade
description: Cotton/Poly Fashion Blend, Reversible, Right hip pocket on both sides, Drawcord closure with easy glide color-coded webbing.

title: Thermometer Digital
description: Compact size - under 5” long, weighs just 11 grams, Range 90.0°F to 109.0°F ±.2°F or 32.0°C to 42.9°C ±.1°C, depending upon scale selection, Reads in as little as 30 seconds (typical response time 30-40 seconds), Replaceable 1.55V (LR41) type battery provides up to 4,500 measurements, Scabbard carry case keeps instrument sanitary, Meets the accuracy requirements for intermittent thermometers under ASTM E1112.

title: Protective Face Shield
description: Full coverage wrap-around face shields are made from polyethylene terephthalate plastic and are designed to prevent exposure to liquid splash, spit, chemicals, and sneeze droplets. Waterproof, latex-free, and dust resistant, the Face Shields offer high quality, 180 degree protection in home, dental, educational, and commercial settings. Face Shields meet the ANSI z87.1 standard.
